{"id":2,"parent_id":0,"book_id":22625,"content_id":1,"language_id":0,"display_order":2,"title":"Blessings of Prayer","subtitle":"","short_title":"Blessings of Prayer","uri":"/new-era/2013/01/blessings-of-prayer","content":[["div",{"id":"head1","uri":"/new-era/2013/01/blessings-of-prayer.head1"},[".title","Blessings of Prayer"],[".kicker","Heavenly Father promises great blessings to those who pray."]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"f1","uri":"/new-era/2013/01/blessings-of-prayer.f1"},[".credit",["div",{"id":"p3","uri":"/new-era/2013/01/blessings-of-prayer.p3"},"Photo illustration by Leslie Nilsson"]]],["div",{"id":"p4","uri":"/new-era/2013/01/blessings-of-prayer.p4"},"As you probably know, we are blessed if we keep the commandments (see",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.20-21"},"D&C 130:20–21"],"). After all, the Lord gives us instruction so that we can have joy. But what does it mean to be blessed? Sometimes we may think of blessings in such general, vague terms that they lose part of their significance. But every commandment brings you specific blessings when you live it."],["div",{"id":"p5","uri":"/new-era/2013/01/blessings-of-prayer.p5"},"For example, have you thought about the blessings Heavenly Father sends you when you pray? If you search the scriptures, you might be surprised at how many blessings are waiting for you because you pray! Just look up “Prayer, Pray” in the Topical Guide."],["div",{"id":"p6","uri":"/new-era/2013/01/blessings-of-prayer.p6"},"To the right you’ll see some of the blessings promised to you if you’re diligent in prayer, as well as the scriptures where you can read more about them."],["div",{"id":"p7","uri":"/new-era/2013/01/blessings-of-prayer.p7"},"So, the next time you hear someone say that you’ll be blessed for keeping the commandment to pray always (see",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.15,18"},"3 Nephi 18:15, 18"],";",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/61.39"},"D&C 61:39"],"), remember that it’s more than just a phrase. Heavenly Father has specific blessings set aside for His faithful children, and often, we simply need to ask for them and live worthy of them."],["h3","Forgiveness"],["ul.bullet",["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/enos/1.4-5"},"Enos 1:4–5"]]],["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.17"},"Alma 34:17"]]],["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.1"},"D&C 90:1"]]]],["h3","Blessings for your family"],["ul.bullet",["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.21"},"3 Nephi 18:21"]]]],["h3","Ability to overcome temptation"],["ul.bullet",["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.39"},"Alma 34:39"]]],["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.5"},"D&C 10:5"]]],["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.33"},"D&C 20:33"]]]],["h3","Confidence to enter God’s presence"],["ul.bullet",["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/21.36"},"Luke 21:36"]]],["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/33.17"},"D&C 33:17"]]]],["h3","Actions that are consecrated"],["ul.bullet",["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/32.9"},"2 Nephi 32:9"]]]],["h3","Strength—that ye faint not"],["ul.bullet",["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/75.11"},"D&C 75:11"]]],["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.126"},"D&C 88:126"]]]],["h3","Wisdom"],["ul.bullet",["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/james/1.5"},"James 1:5"]]],["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.45-46"},"Alma 5:45–46"]]],["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/32.4"},"D&C 32:4"]]]],["h3","Guidance and revelation through the Holy Ghost"],["ul.bullet",["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/17.3"},"Alma 17:3"]]],["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/37.37"},"Alma 37:37"]]],["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/19.8"},"D&C 19:8"]]],["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.13-14"},"D&C 42:13–14"]]]],["h3","Protection"],["ul.bullet",["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/37.37"},"Alma 37:37"]]],["li",["span.label","•"],[".para",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.24"},"D&C 90:24"]]]]]],"refs":null}
